<i>adverb</i>: 훈훈히 [훈훈히], 푸근히 [푸근히], 포근히 [포근히], 알뜰히 [알뜰히], 뜨뜻이 [뜨뜨시], 뜨듯이 [뜨드시], 따사로이 [따사로이], 따뜻이 [따뜨시], 따듯이 [따드시], 따끈히 [따끈히], 따끈따끈 [따끈따끈] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>훈훈히 [훈훈히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. warmly; balmily</dd><br>
<dd>날씨나 온도가 견디기 좋을 만큼 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of the weather or temperature being bearably warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. warmly; warm-heartedly</dd><br>
<dd>마음을 부드럽게 녹여 주는 따뜻함이 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of having warmth that softens the heart.</dd><br>
<dd>3. in the state of filling the air</dd><br>
<dd>냄새가 서려 있는 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a smell filling the air, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푸근히 [푸근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily; snugly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 부드럽고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a quite thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 부드럽고 따뜻하여 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a feeling or atmosphere being comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 꽤 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In windless and quite warm weather.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>포근히 [포근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily; snugly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 보드랍고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 보드랍고 따뜻하여 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a feeling or atmosphere being comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In windless and quite warm weather.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>알뜰히 [알뜰히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. frugally; thriftily</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 살림을 규모 있고 계획성 있게 하여 빈틈이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of keeping the finance of one's household or business well planned and managed.</dd><br>
<dd>2. warmly; tenderly; deeply</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람을 아끼고 위하는 마음이 진실하고 지극하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With sincere and faithful mind in treating someone kindly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>뜨뜻이 [뜨뜨시]</dt><br>
<dd>warmly</dd><br>
<dd>뜨겁지 않을 정도로 온도가 적당히 높게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an appropriately high temperature, not high to the extent in which it is hot.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>뜨듯이 [뜨드시]</dt><br>
<dd>warmly</dd><br>
<dd>뜨겁지 않을 정도로 온도가 적당히 높게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an appropriately high temperature, not high to the extent in which it is hot.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따사로이 [따사로이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pretty warmly</dd><br>
<dd>따뜻한 기운이 조금 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>With some warmth.</dd><br>
<dd>2. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 다정하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a kind heart.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따뜻이 [따뜨시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. warm; warmly</dd><br>
<dd>아주 덥지 않고 기분 좋은 정도로 알맞게 높은 온도로.</dd><br>
<dd>In an appropriately high temperature that is pleasing, not too hot.</dd><br>
<dd>2. warmly; kindly</dd><br>
<dd>마음, 감정, 태도, 분위기 등이 정답고 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With an affectionate and comfortable state of mind, feeling, attitude, atmosphere, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따듯이 [따드시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>아주 덥지 않고 기분 좋은 정도로 알맞게 높은 온도로.</dd><br>
<dd>In an appropriate, pleasant temperature, which is not too high.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>마음, 감정, 태도, 분위기 등이 정답고 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a loving and comfortable state of mind, having such emotions or attitude, or being in such an atmosphere, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따끈히 [따끈히]</dt><br>
<dd>warm; warmly</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 따뜻하고 더운 느낌이 나게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that something is quite warm and hot.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따끈따끈 [따끈따끈]</dt><br>
<dd>warmly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 따뜻하고 더운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very warm and hot state.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>